the time that remains is a 2009 semi-biographical drama film written and directed by palestinian director elia suleiman . the film stars ali &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; , elia suleiman , saleh bakri and samar &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; . it gives an account of the creation of the israeli state from 1948 to the present . suleiman participated in the 2009 cannes film festival , as his new film competed in the official selection category . the time that remains was also screened at the 2009 toronto international film festival . in november 2009 , the film won the jury grand prize ( with about &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; ) at the asia pacific screen awards . the film won the critics prize of the argentinian film critics association at mar del plata international film festival .